<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 14:21:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Circle 第一季度收入增长 20%，净利润下降</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-11/circle-s-first-quarter-revenue-increases-20-net-income-drops</link><description>Circle Internet Group Inc. 第一季度收入增长 20%，但净利润下降，因为加密货币市场的持续波动扰乱了年初整个行业公司的盈利。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iHMGucUQHtCk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 10:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-11/circle-s-first-quarter-revenue-increases-20-net-income-drops</guid></item><item><title>DRW 支持的数字资产融资估值达 20 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-10/drw-backed-digital-asset-raising-money-at-2-billion-valuation</link><description>据知情人士透露，Digital Asset Holdings LLC 是多家大型银行和贸易公司使用的区块链背后的公司，正在从 a16z 加密货币等投资者那里筹集资金，估值约为 20 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itP.2DcQvYBo/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 11:37:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-10/drw-backed-digital-asset-raising-money-at-2-billion-valuation</guid></item><item><title>参议员关注具有里程碑意义的数字资产法案，银行和加密货币支持者发生争执</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-09/banks-and-crypto-backers-tussle-as-senators-eye-stablecoin-bill</link><description>随着参议院一个重要小组开始考虑一项具有里程碑意义的数字资产法案，银行集团正在最后一刻对稳定币收益率进行妥协。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWhBANxj4P6o/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 23:50:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-09/banks-and-crypto-backers-tussle-as-senators-eye-stablecoin-bill</guid></item></channel></rss>